类 DataPackageProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable

  • 直接已知子类:
    ReaderDataPackageProcess

    public abstract class DataPackageProcess
extends java.util.Observable
    The return data process class.This class resolve the return data package to find the information you want to get.The method analyData(byte[]) receive the complete data package returned by module. Then you can process the data package by yourself.The default implement is (RFID Reader) #TDScannerDataPackageProcess(2D Scanner) #ODScannerDataPackageProcess(1D Scanner)
